# Install arduino bossa

[Arduino BOSSA with nrf52 support](https://github.com/arduino/BOSSA)

# Using bossac for flashing
Press rapid two times the reset button, blink orange led slowly

## Building
```bash
cargo objcopy --release -- -O binary target/arduino-nano33blesense-embassy.bin
```

## Flashing (on openocd host)
```bash
~/development/github/arduino-bossa/bin/bossac -i -d -p /dev/ttyACM1 -e -w -v target/arduino-nano33blesense-embassy.bin -R
```

# GPIO
## Serial UART
| Pin | GPIO  | Board Pin | Mode |
| :-- | :---- | :-------: | :--: |
| RX  | P1.10 | D1/RX     | RX   |
| TX  | P1.03 | D0/TX     | TX   |

## Logging UART
| Pin | GPIO  | Board Pin | Mode |
| :-- | :---- | :-------: | :--: |
| RX  | P1.11 | ~D2       | RX   |
| TX  | P1.12 | ~D3       | TX   |

## Leds
| Led   | GPIO  | Description        |
| :---- | :---- | :----------------- |
| Green | P0.16 | Running            |
| Red   | P0.24 | Invalid input data |
| Blue  | P0.06 | Unsupported day    |